 3^{2k} - 1 = (9-1) (1+3^2+\cdots + 3^{2k-2}) 
3^2 \equiv 1 \pmod 8 \implies 3^{2n} \equiv (3^2)^n \equiv 1^n \equiv 1 \pmod 8
